mares\u003c/a\u003e (Neptune), Deep Stone Crypt (Europa)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeb. 25\u003c/strong\u003e: Vault of Glass (Legends), \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-guide-walkthrough/23859673/crotas-end-raid-walkthrough\"\u003eCrota’s End\u003c/a\u003e (Legends)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMarch 4\u003c/strong\u003e: Last Wish (The Dreaming City), Vow of the Disciple (Savathun’s Throne World)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMarch 11\u003c/strong\u003e: King’s Fall (Legends), Garden of Salvation (Moon)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eA pattern has not yet been set in Heresy. We’re keeping featured raids from previous weeks listed for posterity.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"FEB8L6\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDestiny 2 dungeon rotation this week\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419812/2023_Warlord_s_Ruin_Dungeon_Press_Kit_Dungeon_COMPRESSED_005.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Guardians take on a big Ogre in Destiny 2’s Warlord’s of Ruin dungeon\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419812/2023_Warlord_s_Ruin_Dungeon_Press_Kit_Dungeon_COMPRESSED_005.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asse