er-symbols\"\u003eSundered Doctrine\u003c/a\u003e, does not feature in the rotation and won’t appear as a featured dungeon until a new dungeon comes out.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeb. 11\u003c/strong\u003e: Ghost of the Deep (Legends), Pit of Heresy (Moon)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeb. 18\u003c/strong\u003e: Prophecy (Legends), \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-guide-walkthrough/23985733/warlords-ruin-dungeon-walkthrough-cell-puzzle-solution-secret-chest-locations\"\u003eWarlord’s Ruin\u003c/a\u003e (EDZ)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeb. 25\u003c/strong\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-guide-walkthrough/22823677/grasp-of-avarice-burdened-by-riches-puzzle-escorch-cannons-ncoutner-boss-traps-gjallarhorn\"\u003eGrasp of Avarice\u003c/a\u003e (Cosmodrome)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMarch 4\u003c/strong\u003e: Duality (Moon), The Shattered Throne (The Dreaming City)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMarch 11\u003c/strong\u003e: Spire of the Watcher (Savathun’s Throne World), Prophecy (Legends)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eA pattern has not yet been set in Heresy. We’re keeping featured raids from previous weeks listed for posterity.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"ToPv9T\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat does it mean for a raid and dungeon to be featured?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Six Guardians square off against Oryx in Destiny 2\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25419817/2022_KingsFall_Raid_Press_Kit_Oryx_Compressed_003.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Bungie\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eDestiny 2\u003c/em\u003e has a series of activity types that rotate each week, but the most consequential ones are the endgame activities: \u003cstrong\u003eraids \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003edungeons\u003c/strong\u003e. If you’re new to Destiny, raids are six-player activities that are widely considered to be the most difficult content in the game. Dungeons are like smaller, simpler raids and only require three Guardians to complete (and, with practice, and can even be completed solo).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen a raid or dungeon is featured, you’ll get a \u003cstrong\u003ePinnacle Power\u003c/strong\u003e piece of loot when you complete the activity, and you can complete encounters over and over again for a chance at loot. This means that when, for example, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-forsaken-guide/2018/9/18/17872542/last-wish-raid-kalli-the-corrupted\"\u003eLast Wish\u003c/a\u003e raid is featured, you can dive in and complete each encounter multiple times to unlock a weapon pattern you’ve been dying to get. This is a big shift from normal raids, which will typically only give you loot once per week.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe featured raids and dungeons will rotate out and a new one will rotate in each Tuesday. Finally, it’s worth noting that \u003cstrong\u003ethe most recent raid and dungeon added to the game can never be featured\u003c/strong\u003e, although they offer pinnacle gear every single week.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe most recent raid in \u003cem\u003eDestiny 2\u003c/em\u003e is \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-guide-walkthrough/24175263/salvations-edge-raid-steps-encounters-witness-boss-fight-how-to-beat\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSalvation’s Edge\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e — \u003c/strong\u003eadded in \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/destiny-2-the-final-shape/40815\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eThe Final Shape\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003cstrong\u003e—\u003c/strong\u003e and the most recent dungeon is \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/destiny-2-guide-walkthrough/521312/sundered-doctrine-dungeon-guide-walkthrough-encounter-symbols\"\u003eSundered Doctrine\u003c/a\u003e — \u003c/strong\u003eadded in Episode: Heresy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
